sequenceDiagram
participant C as Client Process<br/>(App)
participant CP as Proxy / BinderProxy<br/>(Java + Native)
participant K as Binder Driver<br/>(Kernel)
participant SP as BBinder / Stub<br/>(Java + Native)
participant S as Server Process<br/>(SystemServer)

Note over C,S: 阶段1: Client 发起调用
C->>CP: IXxxService.method(args)
CP->>CP: Parcel.writeInterfaceToken()<br/>Parcel.writeXxx(args)
CP->>K: ioctl(BINDER_WRITE_READ)<br/>[BC_TRANSACTION + data]

Note over K: 阶段2: 内核处理
K->>K: binder_transaction()<br/>① 在 target 的 mmap 区域分配 buffer<br/>② copy_from_user()【一次拷贝】<br/>③ 将事务挂到 target 的 todo 队列
K->>SP: 唤醒 Server Binder 线程<br/>[BR_TRANSACTION]

Note over SP,S: 阶段3: Server 处理请求
SP->>SP: IPCThreadState::executeCommand()<br/>→ BBinder::transact()<br/>→ JavaBBinder::onTransact() [JNI]
SP->>S: Stub.onTransact()<br/>→ 分发到具体 method() 实现
S->>SP: 返回结果<br/>reply.writeXxx()
SP->>K: ioctl(BINDER_WRITE_READ)<br/>[BC_REPLY + reply]

Note over K: 阶段4: 内核传递 Reply
K->>K: binder_transaction()<br/>copy_from_user()【reply 拷贝】
K->>CP: 唤醒 Client 线程<br/>[BR_REPLY]

Note over C,CP: 阶段5: Client 收到结果
CP->>CP: reply.readXxx()
CP->>C: 返回调用结果
